Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Day’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday afternoon’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Day” game were:
01-02-05-07-10-11-12-15-16-18-21-23
(one, two, five, seven, ten, eleven, twelve, fifteen, sixteen, eighteen, twenty-one, twenty-three)
